soft-review-tracklist-lyrics-3756826">Hit Me Hard and Soft</a> 》上榜。当<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-billie-eilish-guess-remix-the-dare-finneas-3780251">两位艺术家联手创作《Guess》</a>时，斯威夫特立即发行了专辑的另一个变体，正如她的评论家所预测的那样。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/raye-holly-humberstone-suki-waterhouse-and-more-confirmed-to-support-taylor-swift-for-final-wembley-eras-shows-3781049">Raye、Holly Humberstone、Suki Waterhouse 等人确认将支持泰勒·斯威夫特在温布利“Eras”最后一场演出，该消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
聆听 Mark Lanegan 之前未发行的歌曲“Heard A Train” https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-previously-unreleased-mark-lanegan-song-heard-a-train-3781052?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=listen-to-previously-unreleased-马克·拉尼根听到火车之歌Poppy BurtonMon, 05 Aug 2024 14:48:21 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3781052 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/mark-lanegan.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="马克·莱根" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/mark-lanegan.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/mark-lanegan-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/mark-lanegan-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/mark-lanegan-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/mark-lanegan-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/mark-lanegan-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 《Bubblegum XX》将于 8 月 23 日登陆 Beggars Arkive</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-previously-unreleased-mark-lanegan-song-heard-a-train-3781052">聆听马克·兰根 (Mark Lanegan) 之前未发行的歌曲“Heard A Train”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/mark-lanegan.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="马克·莱根" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/mark-lanegan.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/mark-lanegan-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/mark-lanegan-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/mark-lanegan-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/mark-lanegan-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/mark-lanegan-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mark-lanegan">马克·莱根 (Mark Lanegan) 之前未发行的歌曲</a>《Heard a Train》已在《Bubblegum》重新发行之前发行。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/mark-lanegan-obituary-tribute-3167245">Mark Lanegan，1964 – 2022：现代另类摇滚的基石</a></strong></li></ul><p>早在七月，已故<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-screaming-trees">尖叫树</a>主唱的社交媒体帐户上就分享了一篇帖子， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mark-lanegans-social-media-accounts-appear-to-tease-posthumous-new-release-3772992">首次暗示可能会在死后发行</a>。</p><p> “我们感谢您在过去两年中的善意和爱心之言。很快就有很多消息要与您分享。”这篇文章的标题是，这是自 2022 年兰根去世以来，他的社交媒体账户上首次分享的消息。</p><p>然后，兰尼根（Lanegan）的庄园宣布，将发布“泡泡糖”盒装，以庆祝专辑的20周年纪念日，并包括12首以前未发行的歌曲。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="听到火车（2024年再生）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/y_B_9DhmCBU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>现在，可以流媒体播放2004年专辑“ Heard A Train”。</p><p> “ Bubblegum XX”将于8月23日通过乞g集团目录和档案部的Beggars Arkive到达。这张专辑的重新制作的双LP版以及40个掌握曲目的4XLP/3XCD/数字发行版。</p><p>不仅如此，4xLP盒子还包含一本64页的精装书，其中包含兰尼根（Lanegan）的前合作者的论文，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queens-of-the-stone-age">石器时代乐队的皇后</a>乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/josh-homme">Josh Homme</a>和Troy van Leeuwen，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/duff-mckagan">Duff McKagan</a>和Greg Dulli的像。它还包含Steve Gullick的工作室笔记和以前看不见的照片。</p><p>正如Homme在他已故合作者的演示和未发行的曲目中所指出的那样：“马克的早期独奏作品无可否认的强大。他们阴沉，脆弱，令人叹为观止，美丽，比其他人更真实。”</p><p>兰根打算让<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beck">贝克</a>出现在“联合墓碑”上，但是当时，贝克正在制作自己的专辑，因此他将其放在一边。但是，他在今年的曲目中增加了人声和口琴。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mark-lanegans-estate-announces-bubblegum-20th-anniversary-box-set-3773381"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>您可以找到有关“ BubbleGum XX”的更多信息，并<a href="https://shop.beggarsarkive.com/release/463840-mark-lanegan-bubblegum-xx" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订。</p></div></div><p>该帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-previously-unreleased-mark-lanegan-song-heard-a-train-3781052">听取了以前未发行的马克·兰尼根（Mark Lanegan）歌曲“ Heard A Train”的声音，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
